  "3066570": {
    "name": "青天井",
    "steam_appid": 3066570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a252fd1e19ce3a92c2648391ab650b62.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入《青天井》的世界，在这里，古老的麻将游戏与策略深度的卡牌构筑相结合。利用各类独特的遗物，掌握复杂的役种，并运用特殊的牌面增幅来迎战各路心魔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/1eff7c5de80f52199902e5222e1e3a34.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/1eff7c5de80f52199902e5222e1e3a34.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/1eff7c5de80f52199902e5222e1e3a34.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/d4b599a08623328cb3b99f4d7c9d71c1.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有超过100种役种和144种独特的遗物，你的每一手牌都能触发最不可思议的联动。在合适的时机使用合适的道具，篡改牌面，绝境逢生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/07a2d94fe3fd016c25e672bc1b08c756.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/07a2d94fe3fd016c25e672bc1b08c756.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/07a2d94fe3fd016c25e672bc1b08c756.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/0deeeff4fe5905b463707b97198e401e.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全随机生成关卡，遗物，道具和增幅，无尽的可能。调整策略，让你的每一次青天井之旅都不一样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/802690c1d517cb1df4c3837a53a684e8.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/802690c1d517cb1df4c3837a53a684e8.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/802690c1d517cb1df4c3837a53a684e8.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/26f8c599209bb85ce84b9c0d9f76424b.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从超过四十种不同的麻将风格中汲取灵感，并制作成了不同的麻将机制。无论你是麻将新手、立直麻将玩家，还是国标麻将玩家，都可以在青天井里找到适合自己中意的牌组。定缺？没问题！宝牌？当然有！花牌？不用说了，我们应有尽有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/ab66444d48b41ced7bfd5c06d1f3807c.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/ab66444d48b41ced7bfd5c06d1f3807c.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/ab66444d48b41ced7bfd5c06d1f3807c.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/58954b44b05b61cc4169bb6751d025da.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌控遗物：</strong> 解锁并运用144种独特的遗物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>番种多样：</strong> 探索并激活多于100个不同的番种。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态玩法：</strong> 体验由种子随机生成的变化关卡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多元风格：</strong> 享受来自40多种地区麻将风格的元素。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略深度：</strong> 调整策略以克服强大的心魔BOSS。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/c7c334b960e3dde74457a90084be5551.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p>",
